snippet.title: ＲＥＳＰＩＴＥ　２．０　－　Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available October 11, 2019
https://modus-interactive.itch.io/respite
===================================================
ＲＥＳＰＩＴＥ　２．０
===================================================

=-Take control of an esoteric piece of software-=
 
=-Over 20 UNIQUE LOCALES to discover-=

=-Branching paths result in a NEW JOURNEY each time you embark-=

=-Relaxing, HIGH FIDELITY MUSIC tracks to put your mind at ease-=

=-Variable SPEED CONTROLS enable you to travel at your own pace-=

Find your ＲＥＳＰＩＴＥ today!

===================================================

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ModusPwnin
Find more games at: https://modus-interactive.itch.io

Trailer by:
Catherine Brinegar
https://cbrinegar.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/cathroon
